name: "Demonz" by Ramenyanen (me). Card 8. Keiko.
description: "Demonz" is a collection of demons, demon hunters, stoners, angels and others. The eighth one (8 of 100) is Keiko. Keiko is a bounty hunter and demon slayer (a demon which slays other demons yes!). The biggest trouble of hell! Collect them all!
